title: Golfer makes double eagle
maintext:
BARBOURSVILLE — Tyler Blankenship made a double eagle Friday afternoon at the Esquire Golf Course.
Blankenship used a driver and an 8-iron on the 504-yard, par-5 third hole. Roger Keyser and Larry Turley witnessed the shot.
